	<!--  Liberty Prime   -->
	<ThingDef ParentName="RobCo_LibertyPrimeBase">
		<defName>RobCo_LibertyPrime</defName>
		<label>Liberty Prime</label>
		<description>A massive pre-war war machine jointly developed by RobCo Industries, General Atomics International, and Mass Fusion for the United States Army. It stands approximately twenty meters tall and is equipped with twin head-mounted energy cannons and a supply of tactical nuclear bombs for destroying fortified positions. Originally designed to liberate Anchorage from Chinese forces, it was never deployed before the Great War due to power supply failures.</description>
	</ThingDef>
	<PawnKindDef ParentName="RobCo_HugeRobotKind">
		<defName>RobCo_LibertyPrime</defName>
		<label>Liberty Prime</label>
		<pawnDesc>A colossal pre-war war machine jointly developed by RobCo Industries, General Atomics International, and Mass Fusion for the United States Army. Standing roughly twenty meters tall and weighing hundreds of tons, Liberty Prime was designed to liberate Anchorage, Alaska from Chinese occupation. Pre-war power supply failures kept it from deployment until the Brotherhood of Steel reactivated it in 2277. Its twin head-mounted energy beams can slag vehicles in seconds, and it carries an inexhaustible supply of tactical nuclear bombs to level fortified positions. Between attacks it delivers thunderous anti-communist propaganda. No known conventional weapon can destroy it in open combat — only orbital bombardment has proven effective against a fully operational unit.</pawnDesc>
		<race>RobCo_LibertyPrime</race>
		<combatPower>1200</combatPower>
